00:39:10,271 --> 00:39:14,330
Rym: So when you plug a lamp in, how do you not accidentally create a voltage loop?

758
00:39:16,473 --> 00:39:17,306
Scott: Because it just is.

759
00:39:18,091 --> 00:39:18,623
Rym: What do you mean?

760
00:39:18,684 --> 00:39:18,889
Rym: it just is?

761
00:39:19,712 --> 00:39:20,749
Rym: So I got a lamp.

