00:43:54,211 --> 00:43:55,410
Scott: There's not anything wrong with it.

854
00:43:55,490 --> 00:43:56,929
Scott: It's just unnecessarily large.

855
00:43:57,310 --> 00:44:04,407
Rym: So your typical USB cable you use to charge your phone is USB-A to USB micro-B.

856
00:44:05,870 --> 00:44:08,069
Rym: But Black Dynamite, isn't there a micro-A?

