899
00:47:15,630 --> 00:47:16,314
Rym: Exactly.

900
00:47:16,375 --> 00:47:19,310
Rym: So usually the only way to tell is that a USB 3 port-- Are blue.

901
00:47:19,670 --> 00:47:21,470
Rym: --tend to be blue, but that's not required.

902
00:47:21,590 --> 00:47:23,730
Scott: It's not required, but it's sort of a helpful thing, right?

903
00:47:23,750 --> 00:47:25,902
Scott: I think USB 2-- Everything I have that's USB 3 is blue.

904
00:47:26,891 --> 00:47:28,590
Scott: Even the USB stick I bought is blue.

905
00:47:29,012 --> 00:47:33,930
